<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 20:05:58 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>研究人员推断，西班牙的尼安德特人引发了火灾</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-22/ty-article/neanderthals-in-spain-started-the-fire-researchers-deduce/0000018b-57c2-d2b2-addf-77fa1d650000</link><description>我们知道古人类使用火已有数十万年，甚至超过一百万年，但他们能点燃火吗？尼安德特人可以</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 18:54:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-10-22/ty-article/neanderthals-in-spain-started-the-fire-researchers-deduce/0000018b-57c2-d2b2-addf-77fa1d650000</guid></item><item><title>数千名艺术界人士发出信函谴责以色列，但没有提及哈马斯的屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/art-world-figures-issue-letter-denouncing-israel-failing-to-mention-hamas-massacre/0000018b-57f6-d2b2-addf-77feb0120000</link><description>艺术家、画廊主和其他艺术界成员发表了这封公开信，其中展示了一位嘲笑以色列人质的艺术家的作品。 1,000 名艺术家（其中大多数是以色列人）回应道：“你让我们所有人失去人性”</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 18:14:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/art-world-figures-issue-letter-denouncing-israel-failing-to-mention-hamas-massacre/0000018b-57f6-d2b2-addf-77feb0120000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境社区的幸存者对政府代表不请自来访问他们的基布兹感到愤怒</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/survivors-in-israeli-border-community-angered-by-uninvited-visits-by-govt-reps/0000018b-57b0-d2b2-addf-77f818d90000</link><description>贝埃里基布兹 (Kibbutz Be&amp;#39;eri) 的一名居民表示，“他们知道我们不希望他们来，但他们还是来了。”哈马斯 10 月 7 日的残酷袭击造成至少 112 人死亡。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 17:57:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/survivors-in-israeli-border-community-angered-by-uninvited-visits-by-govt-reps/0000018b-57b0-d2b2-addf-77f818d90000</guid></item><item><title>国防官员担心内塔尼亚胡任命的负责加沙以色列人质的人可能会损害家人的信任</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-fear-netanyahus-appointee-on-gaza-hostages-could-harm-families-trust/0000018b-57f8-d8e2-a1eb-f7fe8cb50000</link><description>国防部消息人士批评加尔·赫希与哈马斯最近释放的两名人质合影的决定以及他上周对外国大使的长篇大论</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 17:02:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/defense-officials-fear-netanyahus-appointee-on-gaza-hostages-could-harm-families-trust/0000018b-57f8-d8e2-a1eb-f7fe8cb50000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯扣押的人质：从以色列被绑架的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/hostages-held-by-hamas-the-names-of-those-abducted-from-israel/0000018b-55f8-d5d2-afef-d5fdd04e0000</link><description>10 月 7 日，超过 200 人——以色列人和非以色列人、婴儿、妇女和老人、平民和士兵——被哈马斯恐怖分子俘虏，并被武力带到加沙。以下是所有经官方确认的人质姓名</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 16:41:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/hostages-held-by-hamas-the-names-of-those-abducted-from-israel/0000018b-55f8-d5d2-afef-d5fdd04e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列对加沙长达16年的封锁失败了。这真的是唯一的选择吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-16-year-blockade-of-gaza-failed-was-it-really-the-only-option/0000018b-57f3-d2b2-addf-77fb07f60000</link><description>许多以色列分析人士一致认为，封锁加沙是对付哈马斯的唯一途径。但 10 月 7 日的灾难性袭击引发了严峻的问题：封锁政策是否是以色列的另一个重要战略误解</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 16:40:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/israels-16-year-blockade-of-gaza-failed-was-it-really-the-only-option/0000018b-57f3-d2b2-addf-77fb07f60000</guid></item><item><title>“携带枪支，这是救星：本格维尔和他的妻子吹嘘以色列携带武器的人数急剧增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-his-wife-boast-of-arming-jewish-israelis/0000018b-5753-d473-a5fb-77db1c2d0000</link><description>上周，以色列议会国家安全委员会批准了国家安全部长本-格维尔提出的枪支许可证规定修正案，以便在南部战事持续不断的情况下，获得许可证的条件更加宽松</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 15:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/ben-gvir-and-his-wife-boast-of-arming-jewish-israelis/0000018b-5753-d473-a5fb-77db1c2d0000</guid></item><item><title>150,000 枚火箭和导弹：以色列在与真主党的战争中将遭遇的武器</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</link><description>根据最新的已知评估，真主党拥有数万枚可深入以色列境内的远程导弹、广泛的防空系统和突击队</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 15:33:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/150-000-rockets-and-missiles-the-weapons-israel-would-encounter-in-a-war-with-hezbollah/0000018b-573d-d2b2-addf-777df6210000</guid></item><item><title>美国高级官员警告以色列-加沙战争中中东局势升级的可能性增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/senior-u-s-officials-warn-about-increasing-escalation-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-57af-d473-a5fb-77ef7d5b0000</link><description>美国国防部长劳埃德·奥斯汀和国务卿安东尼·布林肯认为“局势可能会大幅升级”，担心真主党和伊朗可能与以色列发生直接冲突</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 14:54:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/senior-u-s-officials-warn-about-increasing-escalation-amid-israel-gaza-war/0000018b-57af-d473-a5fb-77ef7d5b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列与哈马斯战争的斗争正在华盛顿升温</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-battle-over-the-israel-hamas-war-is-heating-up-in-washington/0000018b-5735-d2b2-addf-777d25eb0000</link><description>尽管美国总统乔·拜登表示他全力支持以色列，但其官员的行动却描绘出一幅略有不同的景象。华盛顿特区的民主党和共和党内部也出现了第二条战线</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 14:40:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-battle-over-the-israel-hamas-war-is-heating-up-in-washington/0000018b-5735-d2b2-addf-777d25eb0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯、真主党和胡塞武装：伊朗如何卷入以色列-哈马斯战争？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/hamas-hezbollah-and-the-houthis-what-is-irans-involvement-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-4318-d242-abef-533e2d6a0000</link><description>虽然只有一份报告明确将伊朗与 10 月 7 日以色列南部的暴行联系起来，但人们的共识是，伊朗一直在操纵其在加沙、约旦河西岸、黎巴嫩甚至也门的恐怖组织代理人。然后是以色列与沙特阿拉伯关系正常化的小问题</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 13:14:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/hamas-hezbollah-and-the-houthis-what-is-irans-involvement-in-the-israel-hamas-war/0000018b-4318-d242-abef-533e2d6a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对以色列的生存构成生存威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-is-an-existential-threat-to-israels-survival/0000018b-5733-d8e2-a1eb-f737a78b0000</link><description>以色列在国内和国际上的脆弱是伊朗及其代理人以及该国失败的领导人内塔尼亚胡的过错。美国和德国正在提供前所未有的军事、道义和外交支持，以支撑以色列公众，同时也防止加沙地带出现天文数字般的死亡人数</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 12:44:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-10-22/ty-article-opinion/.premium/netanyahu-is-an-existential-threat-to-israels-survival/0000018b-5733-d8e2-a1eb-f737a78b0000</guid></item><item><title>让女性应对以色列-哈马斯战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/women-prove-they-wouldve-handled-israel-hamas-war-better/0000018b-5738-d8e2-a1eb-f73ead300000</link><description>面对以色列与加沙战争期间男性领导力的失败，一些女性因她们的勇敢而闪耀并鼓舞人心 ■ 可惜她们被排除在决策之外</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 12:38:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/women-prove-they-wouldve-handled-israel-hamas-war-better/0000018b-5738-d8e2-a1eb-f73ead300000</guid></item><item><title>乌克兰综合症：为什么西方领导人无法停止访问战时以色列</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-ukraine-syndrome-why-western-leaders-cant-stop-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-569b-dc3c-a5df-debb06080000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡总理可能会很感激有机会会见那些没有指责他破坏自己国家的人，但拜登、马克龙和他的同事们的访问有真正的地缘政治原因。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 11:56:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-ukraine-syndrome-why-western-leaders-cant-stop-visiting-wartime-israel/0000018b-569b-dc3c-a5df-debb06080000</guid></item><item><title>“我们等待他们平安无事的消息。它从未来过&amp;#39;</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-waited-for-a-message-that-yarden-kinneret-and-carmel-were-okay-but-it-never-came/0000018b-568e-df6e-a5db-76ee061b0000</link><description>被哈马斯扣为人质的以色列家庭：一个特别项目 ■ Roni Roman 想象她的姐姐 Yarden 帮助被囚禁的伤员。她的哥哥强迫军队寻找她。他们一起试图了解亚登和她的搭档阿隆的妹妹发生了什么事</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 10:57:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article-magazine/.premium/we-waited-for-a-message-that-yarden-kinneret-and-carmel-were-okay-but-it-never-came/0000018b-568e-df6e-a5db-76ee061b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列自2000年代以来首次使用战机袭击约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-uses-warplane-to-strike-in-west-bank-for-first-time-since-2000s/0000018b-56c3-d02b-a3db-ffdf22400000</link><description>以色列军方表示，杰宁难民营的空袭目标是一个计划重复边境社区大屠杀的恐怖分子。 巴勒斯坦卫生部表示，自 10 月 7 日以来，已有 90 名巴勒斯坦人被以色列的炮火杀害。</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 10:11:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/israel-uses-warplane-to-strike-in-west-bank-for-first-time-since-2000s/0000018b-56c3-d02b-a3db-ffdf22400000</guid></item><item><title>反犹太主义暴露，法国左翼与哈马斯一起自杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-french-left-is-commiting-suicide-along-with-hamas/0000018b-569f-d1d7-ab8b-7edfecb80000</link><description>拒绝谴责哈马斯的残酷杀戮是恐怖行为不仅是反犹太主义，而且为极右翼掌权铺平了道路</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 09:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/the-french-left-is-commiting-suicide-along-with-hamas/0000018b-569f-d1d7-ab8b-7edfecb80000</guid></item><item><title>国防部消息人士称，内塔尼亚胡发起运动，指责以色列军方未能预测哈马斯袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-on-campaign-to-blame-idf-for-failure-to-predict-attack-defense-sources-say/0000018b-5688-d5d2-afef-d6fde37a0000</link><description>以色列总理任命了一名新发言人与军事记者联络，这是一个不寻常的举动，一位消息人士称，他们听说他诽谤军官</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 09:28:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-on-campaign-to-blame-idf-for-failure-to-predict-attack-defense-sources-say/0000018b-5688-d5d2-afef-d6fde37a0000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡对以色列造成了大屠杀。他早就该辞职了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-strategy-to-cling-to-power-wont-save-him-from-an-enduring-legacy-of-failure/0000018b-5640-d5d2-afef-d6fd6ccf0000</link><description>总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡现在指望疲劳和公众的绝望来帮助他保住职位，但不能相信他能够管理一场战争，这也无法让他摆脱持久的失败遗产。当战争结束时，无论是三周还是三个月，所有的政治地狱都会解脱</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 09:28:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-strategy-to-cling-to-power-wont-save-him-from-an-enduring-legacy-of-failure/0000018b-5640-d5d2-afef-d6fd6ccf0000</guid></item><item><title>美军在动荡的中东面临日益严重的威胁，击落导弹和无人机</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/u-s-military-shoots-down-missiles-drones-as-it-faces-growing-threats-in-middle-east/0000018b-5673-dc3c-a5df-defb8e870000</link><description>在多起独立事件中——来自也门的导弹、来自伊拉克和叙利亚的无人机——美军被迫在中东各地采取行动，试图缓和并防止更广泛的冲突</description><pubDate>Sun, 22 Oct 2023 09:03:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-10-22/ty-article/u-s-military-shoots-down-missiles-drones-as-it-faces-growing-threats-in-middle-east/0000018b-5673-dc3c-a5df-defb8e870000</guid></item></channel></rss>